{"tid":2225431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［世紀大和解］日俄首腦會談 菅義偉：希望全面發展日俄關係","createTime":"2020-10-01T10:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T18:26:56.000Z","uid":58841,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac76b8c31a6b11b7b859e46d6b6b982ef35f0c2","tid":2225431,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:17:38.000Z","msg":"日本首相菅義偉29日晚與俄羅斯總統普京舉行了首次電話會談，據日本政府相關人士透露，雙方就繼續推動1956年簽署的《蘇日共同宣言》達成一致，兩國將繼續安倍2018年11月與普京達成的協議、以北方四島中的齒舞羣島和色丹島兩島&ldquo;移交&rdquo;爲核心展開談判。兩國首腦還同意近期直接舉行會談就雙邊關係坦率交換意見。<br />\n<br />\n綜合日本媒體報導，菅義偉於會談中表示，希望全面發展日俄關係，不把北方領土問題推到下一代，將爲此畫上句號。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.soundofhope.org/post/427189?lang=b5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.soundofhope.org%2Fpost%2F427189%3Flang%3Db5&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w18pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=09e184f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.soundofhope.org/post/427189?lang=b5</a><br />\n<br />\n其實俄佬同架仔拗北方四島拗左差唔多70幾年架啦<br />\n如果呢個問題解決左日本極有可能取代契弟中共既地位<br />\n因為契弟比到既野架仔一樣比到<br />\n而且會比得更加好<br />\n係支那而家仲懵盛盛唔知咩事啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9a807ce8612a786231893ba5bd491ebc427e3e","tid":2225431,"uid":94516,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:18:36.000Z","msg":"Share東北三省<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"154b677d0de30db7be00cbc4e0c3311e3c2c6704","tid":2225431,"uid":28397,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7a9a807ce8612a786231893ba5bd491ebc427e3e","tid":2225431,"uid":94516,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:18:36.000Z","msg":"Share東北三省<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-